{"tid":1594764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［入黎！］呢首歌你都一定要聽！","createTime":"2019-09-25T17:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T19:49:15.000Z","uid":135077,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4008cc616fd3913e1f88dd27622cf88098f52ed9","tid":1594764,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"我發現好似冇乜人識呢隻歌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢首歌都好好聽架！仲好有意思添！<br />\n歌手把聲仲要成個陳奕迅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nApple Music都有得聽架！之前仲上過ranking tim!<br />\n但發現愈來都係冇乜聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家比次機會佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地都好比心機唱呢首歌架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢首歌同都香港人作架！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作詞：香港人    作曲：香港人<br />\n編曲：香港人<br />\n<br />\n《和你飛》<br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n<br />\n聽呼喊聲不絕耳嗎 這心痛怎消化<br />\n難道若說怕 就會停火嗎<br />\n炮火擦身傷勢重嗎 還是強撐嗎<br />\n但怕你 沒法回家<br />\n<br />\n困於這街道上團聚 卻失散幽暗角落裡<br />\n我不要毅然別去 背城借一 遠方寄居<br />\n有種愛超越限期盛衰 流在我血脈身體裏<br />\n任雨打 任風吹 我也在這裏<br />\n<br />\n那位唱詩拯救我家 看畫面多優雅<br />\n時局在變化 道理有偏差<br />\n痛哭快失聲似啞巴 流淚來記掛<br />\n為了你 奉上白花<br />\n<br />\n困於這街道上團聚 卻失散幽暗角落裡<br />\n我不要毅然別去 背城借一 遠方寄居<br />\n有種愛超越限期盛衰 流在我血脈身體裏<br />\n任雨打 任風吹 我也在這裏<br />\n<br />\n仍然堅持 愛縱使不易 難道說我們會休止<br />\n<br />\n已經再一夜未能睡 置身這荒誕歲月裡<br />\n抹乾眼淚行下去 要憑兩手刷新壯舉<br />\n有種愛超越限期盛衰 連繫你我內心交瘁<br />\n暴雨打 狂風吹 與你共進退<br />\n<br />\n舊記憶 歷史中 會有著證據<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2UltvQ1nkuM&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=4d3ba53d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM</a><br />\n<br />\n當然唔係叫大家打仗個時唱 搞嘉年華打爭<br />\n只係希望大家做地區快閃同巡迴演唱個時都記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家比次機會佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceef0068769ff1498f4decaa9327f9dbcbaf3e6d","tid":1594764,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7c614be4ad8613e80f23995105d5604f422483c0","tid":1594764,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"一定要聽！"},{"pid":"f1b9ed574f7cabbaa50f0c2452ddbdd6e35afb3a","tid":1594764,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:28:28.000Z","msg":"唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee566ed5f27101d7dd6749e6782a5e922531a4e1","tid":1594764,"uid":264022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:30:54.000Z","msg":"Moov有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74794a66d4059c70acee663663c2c1f6991a911","tid":1594764,"uid":122972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:36:34.000Z","msg":"日日都聽緊 仲有自遊同虛作無聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6293cde99533871eaa21a2f327c136c31300a86f","tid":1594764,"