 />\n<br />\n舊記憶 歷史中 會有著證據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2UltvQ1nkuM&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=4d3ba53d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2UltvQ1nkuM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n當然唔係叫大家打仗個時唱 搞嘉年華打爭<br />\n只係希望大家做地區快閃同巡迴演唱個時都記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家比次機會佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a9066b12a6f73e218cd1676b5146083a0553c725","tid":1594764,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:49:15.000Z","msg":"我超愛呢首"}]}